                     <interp inst="t17730626-38-person496" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
             on the 5th of April. They were deposed to by the prosecutrix.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence.</p>
               <p>I do not know any thing about it.</p>
